---
title: Prawn Wontons, Chicken & Soy Garlic Veggies with Butter Rice & Soy-Chilli Oil
description: These prawn and chicken chive wontons are a fan favourite, and we want to add them to all our recipes! This time we’ve paired them with simple buttery rice with garlic veggies. We’ve also got a sweet and savoury soy chilli oil for you to drizzle over - you won’t need much, it really packs a punch!
